  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1125">
<l>uḷḷuvaṉ maṉyāṉ maṟappiṉ maṟappaṟiyē</l>
<l>ṉoḷḷamark kaṇṇāḷ kuṇam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I had forgotten her who has bright battling eyes, I would have remembered (thee); but I never forget her. (Thus says he to her maid).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
